short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extension for simplifying working with argo workflow logs + link for logs from github

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The extension will open logs automatically for the last failed process. In case that last failed process is trigger-ci, a new tab will be opened and then logs will be open on this tab.
